gle]]'s baseball camps and other special events for high school and club teams annually.  The venue has also hosted the following Mountain West Conference tournaments, NCAA Regional tournaments and NCAA Super Regional tournaments:\n* [[Mountain West Conference Baseball Tournament|MWC Baseball Tournament]]: [[2008 Mountain West Conference Baseball Tournament|2008]], [[2009 Mountain West Conference Baseball Tournament|2009]]\n* [[NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament Regional]]: [[2009 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2009]], [[2010 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2010]], [[2011 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2011]], [[2014 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2014]], [[2015 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2015]], [[2016 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2016]]\n* [[NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament Super Regional]]: [[2014 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament#Fort Worth Super Regional|2014]], [[2015 NCAA Division I Baseball Tournament|2015]]\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of NCAA Division I baseball venues]]\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n{{TCU Horned Frogs baseball navbox}}\n{{Big 12 Conference baseball venue navbox}}\n{{Texas NCAA Division I college baseball venue navbox}}\n\n{{coord|32.703136|-97.372467|type:landmark|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:TCU Horned Frogs baseball venues]]\n[[Category:College baseball venues in the United States]]\n[[Category:Baseball venues in the Dallas\u2013Fort Worth metroplex]]\n[[Category:Baseball venues in Texas]]\n", "name_user": "Iridescent", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eTCU Baseball Attendance:Cleanup andtypo fixing,typo(s) fixed: \u2019s \u2192 's", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lupton_Stadium"}
